{"title":"苗家歌画","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":11,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗家歌画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗：选自贵州、湖南两省的苗族民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画：湖南农民吴成群的“苗岭丰收图”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪个村庄粮不多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公路两旁村庄多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比金钱串葫芦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪个葫芦不盛宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪个村庄粮不多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新开水沟长又长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯弯曲曲流山岗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日日沟水流不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年丰收谷满仓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"薯王"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山腰梯田山下河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山顶红薯种得多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨夜一场倾盆雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把个薯王洗下坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小树压倒几十棵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田坎冲断二十多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“扑通”滚进大河里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水溅起三丈多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员闻声跑来看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来是一条白薯塞断河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窝窝稻谷都称王"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棵石榴四枝丫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千个枝头都开花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要春耕种得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋收准是好庄稼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋风吹来好清凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窝窝稻谷都称“王”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往年几窝割一把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年一窝割几双。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔山闻见谷子香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山歌越唱越新鲜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉花堆集像雪山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘唱歌白云里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难分天上与人间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄庄稼长满坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处响起丰收歌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年粮食挑不完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得用千辆汽车拖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗颗谷子闪金光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔山闻见谷子香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好粮支援工业化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换个铁牛到农庄。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}